entries.femaleVariant: Hey, yeah, sure. Damn, you ol' bastard, been a while since--
Listen to the whole message, please.
Abernathy's purging the dep. Anybody not a hundred percent with her is out.
I'm on her list. No idea why. You know how it is. No prisoners, no dismissals.
Not about to sit around, wait for the executioner. I'm putting together a file. To fuck up her life.
I know you'll know what to do with 'em.
Got all the documents in a, uh, hidey-hole. If I don't manage to make use of 'em, you'll get this message and the coords.
